Alpha & Omega

Alpha & Omega is an engaging math game designed for adults that challenges players to solve arithmetic operations. Players are tasked with entering the correct results for complex calculations, providing a workout for the mind without the pressure of a timer. With intriguing references to the Old Greek language and a mysterious scoring system, this app invites users to ponder its deeper meaning while fostering mathematical skills at their own pace.
